ry setup\\\" into \\\"active build.\\\"\\n\\n**Recommended Next Step:**\\nWe should establish a project baseline. We can do this in two ways:\\n1.  **Architect Questionnaire:** I can walk you through a series of surgical questions to extract the vision for your next app.\\n2.  **Raw Brief:** You can give me a brain dump of what you want to build, and I will draft the initial `APP_BRIEF.md` for your review.\\n\\nWhich path do you want to take?\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\":\"adk-f83c365a-9980-46fe-86a0-6f4b200afce4\",\"args\":{\"skill_name\":\"SESSION_MEMORY_SKILL\"},\"name\":\"invoke_skill\"},{\"id\":\"adk-556e6ff7-0953-41b7-b469-db8c8dafc69e\",\"args\":{\"days\":7},\"name\":\"read_session_memory\"}],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":0.0},\"expected_invocation\":{\"invocation_id\":\"e-bee154d5-8870-4b06-abb0-6d87cd32b750\",\"user_content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"What did we work on recently?\"}],\"role\":\"user\"},\"final_response\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":\"CoEEAY89a18izh0uANLwEi5043pjQ-kQDS-RBQMUF03wMJn07abY0Kv8IMOW0Ug8iC6kZZz3UN0Tpfo19l4W9KecpSVYwgjU1L4tImbi5al5pS8eq1gWR-z3sT8dl-W82EydUrR9dQMLUHnmea64hKdKHzkDfQqLfsGKc9AWyKLDbHs8qs3CU8uOuv-4vgXhQeYvNu0JiZO2NZNbiaDRGJ2aC7w9yQp5GK8z3ksSuM056-QWV0C70yo0j4W66Sg8Vglp5K5YMHR4OFP9RZ8qT0hwWrpXrdc24NYkwNzSAql6L2k_AB7SvoU7XBC8mie21Nki97vHoZL8S2sOaD8eTMm64wGRFu2YO9LORuXG76dhgkkrq9bLVcXEfF1b1eKXLTj8eqgZgafBfXdUMh4rlSpJgKsMFUx_BYmZjX1O9h3UPDX3_nb1FxWk1zFHen37UOyQduON0htOexJbi_lqpOrGSHtOVMMThpwtNo_Jo5QgmRMlu5gmJM50qFapKTm4xhoHnCfMVqNb5ORyuDNgcRg5ZG-R6-50gfTfqChHdI9M8s_7SXYxx9DsrH3KQgCYa6Hw5V2EOkU0QcstEXGDZJQ43cJtgZHZdD1qeWV8RoZY12NUzw5XAf1cL04AE5f3eoWlmRIQ5cjVDKs4RI1K4zBoAQTYCV8LFylTVYAPJQLRU4nA\",\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"It appears we're starting a fresh session for this project, as there are no recent session logs on file for the last 7 days.\\n\\n**What I Hear**\\nYou're looking for a recap of our recent progress before we dive into today's work.\\n\\n**Recommended Next Step**\\nSince I don't see an active **APP_BRIEF** or session history for a specific application build, our first move should be to **establish the project baseline**.\\n\\n**Current State (Based on Factory Context)**\\nWhile we lack a specific project history, our core factory infrastructure is fully established:\\n1.  **Skills Architecture:** We recently finalized the **InvokeSkill** pattern and **Plan Mode** mechanics (documented in the Tier 3 Design Archaeology).\\n2.  **Context Engineering:** The layered context architecture (Identity, Manuals, Session Memory, RAG) is operational.\\n3.  **Core Manuals:** Tier 1 and 2 manuals for Architecture, API design, Database, and the Software Factory Playbook are locked and ready.\\n\\n**Risks / Red Flags**\\n*   **Missing Scope:** Without an `APP_BRIEF.md`, any architectural advice I give will be generic rather than project-specific.\\n*   **Context Gap:** If we *were* working on a specific app and the session files were lost, we need to manually reconstruct the current state.\\n\\n**Action Checklist**\\n1.  **Confirm Project:** Are we starting a brand-new build today?\\n2.  **Run Questionnaire:** If starting new, I'll run the **Architect Questionnaire** (from Tier 2 docs) to extract the raw idea and freeze the intent.\\n3.  **Draft APP_BRIEF:** Generate the initial scope document to lock in the mission and constraints.\\n\\n**Ready to start the ignition questionnaire for a new project, or are we picking up an existing build that I don't have the files for yet?**\"}],\"role\":null},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\