Xiwnv2bXOw2KZwU_W8WuAIINHifBRZBMcqdB88F_TVluBecJkw9VkgO6L-9Od3n1EM6Y_OrormECa7AjgEhwGzF_w7iL9cQRDuzVMGiL8wmreY6v8QQS6BuRGv_6S3ym0_srzHE58WdEw5g--Oj4vXodG51K6bk3mxnvPFtlwLzoRsmdFC917XwK0mWzaPWTN1K88hLn5A7TPmhMC5uT2-UlRMR6rYo79QNXahszQ4sjcMfHvQ73bhg9vc8btdpq9FQioS0VJv_3xCCBRAwy0T\",\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"Picking up from our work over the last 48 hours \u2014 we have successfully established the foundation for this agent and confirmed the session memory protocols are working.\\n\\n**What we've done recently:**\\n*   **Confirmed Factory Grounding:** Verified that the agent is correctly loading its identity and global system instructions.\\n*   **Validated Memory Skills:** Successfully integrated the `SESSION_MEMORY` and `SESSION_UPDATE` skills, ensuring we have continuity between conversations.\\n*   **Status Check:** We confirmed that no active `APP_BRIEF` or project baseline exists yet. You are currently at a clean slate.\\n\\n**Current State:**\\nWe are standing by to move from \\\"factory setup\\\" into \\\"active build.\\\"\\n\\n**Recommended Next Step:**\\nWe should establish a project baseline. We can do this in two ways:\\n1.  **Architect Questionnaire:** I can walk you through a series of surgical questions to extract the vision for your next app.\\n2.  **Raw Brief:** You can give me a brain dump of what you want to build, and I will draft the initial `APP_BRIEF.md` for your review.\\n\\nWhich path do you want to take?\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"grounding_metadata\":null,\"partial\":null,\"turn_complete\":null,\"finish_reason\":\"STOP\",\"error_code\":null,\"error_message\":null,\"interrupted\":null,\"custom_metadata\":null,\"usage_metadata\":{\"cache_tokens_details\":null,\"cached_content_token_count\":null,\"candidates_token_count\":246,\"candidates_tokens_details\":[{\"modality\":\"TEXT\",\"token_count\":246}],\"prompt_token_count\":8799,\"prompt_tokens_details\":[{\